# Cursor AI Indexing Ignore List
# Files/folders listed here won't be indexed by Cursor's AI agents
# This improves performance and reduces irrelevant context

# ====================
# Build Artifacts (Large, Binary, Not Useful for AI)
# ====================
build/
*.zip

# ====================
# Cache & Compiled Files
# ====================
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
*.so

# ====================
# User Data - ALLOWED (User requested visibility)
# ====================
# data_*/ - ALLOWED for agent access
# *.json - ALLOWED for agent access (user data files)

# ====================
# Backups & Archives (Large, Historical)
# ====================
backup_*/
archive_*/
*.backup

# ====================
# Logs - ALLOWED (User requested visibility)
# ====================
# logs/ - ALLOWED for agent access
# *.log - ALLOWED for agent access
*.txt
!version.txt
!requirements.txt
*.spec
!LiteFinPad_v*.spec

# ====================
# Design Assets (Large Images, Not Code)
# ====================
_branding/
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.ico
*.pdn
*.psd

# ====================
# Personal/Internal Notes - ALLOWED (User requested visibility)
# ====================
# _personal/ - ALLOWED for agent access
# docs/internal/ - ALLOWED for agent access
# *_personal* - ALLOWED for agent access
temp_response.txt

# ====================
# Virtual Environments - ALLOWED (User requested visibility)
# ====================
# venv/ - ALLOWED for agent access
# env/ - ALLOWED for agent access
# .venv/ - ALLOWED for agent access
# ENV/ - ALLOWED for agent access

